    {
      "id": "6090ec2daff09e00003db937",
      "text": "Hatena2012-04-23",
      "created": 1335106800,
      "updated": 1335106800,
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e"
    },
    {
      "id": "6090ec2daff09e00003db938",
      "text": "code:hatena",
      "created": 1335106800,
      "updated": 1335106800,
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e"
    },
    {
      "id": "6090ec2daff09e00003db939",
      "text": " <body>",
      "created": 1335106800,
      "updated": 1335106800,
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e"
    },
    {
      "id": "6090ec2daff09e00003db93a",
      "text": " *1335173979*zshに入門する日記",
      "created": 1335106800,
      "updated": 1335106800,
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e"
    },
    {
      "id": "6090ec2daff09e00003db93b",
      "text": " ** 2012-04-23",
      "created": 1335106800,
      "updated": 1335106800,
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e"
    },
    {
      "id": "6090ec2daff09e00003db93c",
      "text": " ",
      "created": 1335106800,
      "updated": 1335106800,
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e"
    },
    {
      "id": "6090ec2daff09e00003db93d",
      "text": " とりあえずMacのTerminal.appの環境設定で、起動時に開くシェルを/bin/zshにした。chshしてもダメだったので。",
      "created": 1335106800,
      "updated": 1335106800,
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e"
    },
    {
      "id": "6090ec2daff09e00003db93e",
      "text": " ",
      "created": 1335106800,
      "updated": 1335106800,
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e"
    },
    {
      "id": "6090ec2daff09e00003db93f",
      "text": " 新しいタブを開いたりした時にちゃんとzshになるようになった。しかし、Lionから入ったと思われる「新しいタブを開く時には同じディレクトリで開く」が機能していない。",
      "created": 1335106800,
      "updated": 1335106800,
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e"
    },
    {
      "id": "6090ec2daff09e00003db940",
      "text": " ",
      "created": 1335106800,
      "updated": 1335106800,
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e"
    },
    {
      "id": "6090ec2daff09e00003db941",
      "text": " http://superuser.com/questions/232835/zsh-open-a-new-tab-in-the-same-directory",
      "created": 1335106800,
      "updated": 1335106800,
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e"
    },
    {
      "id": "6090ec2daff09e00003db942",
      "text": " >||",
      "created": 1335106800,
      "updated": 1335106800,
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e"
    },
    {
      "id": "6090ec2daff09e00003db943",
      "text": " Use Oh-My-Zsh and add the 'osx' plugin in your ~/.zshrc like:",
      "created": 1335106800,
      "updated": 1335106800,
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e"
    },
    {
      "id": "6090ec2daff09e00003db944",
      "text": " ",
      "created": 1335106800,
      "updated": 1335106800,
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e"
    },
    {
      "id": "6090ec2daff09e00003db945",
      "text": " plugins=(git osx)",
      "created": 1335106800,
      "updated": 1335106800,
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e"
    },
    {
      "id": "6090ec2daff09e00003db946",
      "text": " ",
      "created": 1335106800,
      "updated": 1335106800,
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e"
    },
    {
      "id": "6090ec2daff09e00003db947",
      "text": " That's all you need to do!",
      "created": 1335106800,
      "updated": 1335106800,
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e"
    },
    {
      "id": "6090ec2daff09e00003db948",
      "text": " ||<",
      "created": 1335106800,
      "updated": 1335106800,
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e"
    },
    {
      "id": "6090ec2daff09e00003db949",
      "text": " ",
      "created": 1335106800,
      "updated": 1335106800,
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e"
    },
    {
      "id": "6090ec2daff09e00003db94a",
      "text": " Oh!",
      "created": 1335106800,
      "updated": 1335106800,
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e"
    },
    {
      "id": "6090ec2daff09e00003db94b",
      "text": " ",
      "created": 1335106800,
      "updated": 1335106800,
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e"
    },
    {
      "id": "6090ec2daff09e00003db94c",
      "text": " ** oh-my-zsh 導入した",
      "created": 1335106800,
      "updated": 1335106800,
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e"
    },
    {
      "id": "6090ec2daff09e00003db94d",
      "text": " ",
      "created": 1335106800,
      "updated": 1335106800,
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e"
    },
    {
      "id": "6090ec2daff09e00003db94e",
      "text": " カレントディレクトリが持ち越せるようになった。",
      "created": 1335106800,
      "updated": 1335106800,
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e"
    },
    {
      "id": "6090ec2daff09e00003db94f",
      "text": " ",
      "created": 1335106800,
      "updated": 1335106800,
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e"
    },
    {
      "id": "6090ec2daff09e00003db950",
      "text": " でもデフォルトの配色が気に入らないのでテーマはとりあえずsimpleにしたが、それでもプロンプトに非ASCIIを使うのが気に入らない。修正する必要があるな。",
      "created": 1335106800,
      "updated": 1335106800,
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e"
    },
    {
      "id": "6090ec2daff09e00003db951",
      "text": " ",
      "created": 1335106800,
      "updated": 1335106800,
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e"
    },
    {
      "id": "6090ec2daff09e00003db952",
      "text": " ** githubにdotfilesリポジトリを作った",
      "created": 1335106800,
      "updated": 1335106800,
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e"
    },
    {
      "id": "6090ec2daff09e00003db953",
      "text": " ",
      "created": 1335106800,
      "updated": 1335106800,
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e"
    },
    {
      "id": "6090ec2daff09e00003db954",
      "text": " いまさらだけど、やってなかったので。~/.dotfilesにcloneした。",
      "created": 1335106800,
      "updated": 1335106800,
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e"
    },
    {
      "id": "6090ec2daff09e00003db955",
      "text": " ",
      "created": 1335106800,
      "updated": 1335106800,
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e"
    },
    {
      "id": "6090ec2daff09e00003db956",
      "text": " ** minimalをもっとminimalに",
      "created": 1335106800,
      "updated": 1335106800,
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e"
    },
    {
      "id": "6090ec2daff09e00003db957",
      "text": " ",
      "created": 1335106800,
      "updated": 1335106800,
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e"
    },
    {
      "id": "6090ec2daff09e00003db958",
      "text": " themeのなかにあったminimalから僕が余計だと思う機能をそぎ落としてだいぶシンプルになった。さすがにワークツリーがdirtyであることの表示とかブランチの表示は残しておいたけど、それがカラフルである必要は感じない。",
      "created": 1335106800,
      "updated": 1335106800,
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e"
    },
    {
      "id": "6090ec2daff09e00003db959",
      "text": " ",
      "created": 1335106800,
      "updated": 1335106800,
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e"
    },
    {
      "id": "6090ec2daff09e00003db95a",
      "text": " [f:id:nishiohirokazu:20120423190933p:image]",
      "created": 1335106800,
      "updated": 1335106800,
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e"
    },
    {
      "id": "6090ec2daff09e00003db95b",
      "text": " ",
      "created": 1335106800,
      "updated": 1335106800,
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e"
    },
    {
      "id": "6090ec2daff09e00003db95c",
      "text": " たぶん状況によってはもっと色々情報を出したい時とかあると思うけど、そういうのはそういう時に明示的にやる。デフォルトでいっぱい出されると疲れてしまう。",
      "created": 1335106800,
      "updated": 1335106800,
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e"
    },
    {
      "id": "6090ec2daff09e00003db95d",
      "text": " ",
      "created": 1335106800,
      "updated": 1335106800,
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e"
    },
    {
      "id": "6090ec2daff09e00003db95e",
      "text": " ** タイトルを変更させない",
      "created": 1335106800,
      "updated": 1335106800,
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e"
    },
    {
      "id": "6090ec2daff09e00003db95f",
      "text": " ",
      "created": 1335106800,
      "updated": 1335106800,
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e"
    },
    {
      "id": "6090ec2daff09e00003db960",
      "text": " cdの時に勝手にタイトルを変えるのをやめさせる。タイトルは自分で設定したいのだ。",
      "created": 1335106800,
      "updated": 1335106800,
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e"
    },
    {
      "id": "6090ec2daff09e00003db961",
      "text": " ",
      "created": 1335106800,
      "updated": 1335106800,
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e"
    },
    {
      "id": "6090ec2daff09e00003db962",
      "text": " >||",
      "created": 1335106800,
      "updated": 1335106800,
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e"
    },
    {
      "id": "6090ec2daff09e00003db963",
      "text": " DISABLE_AUTO_TITLE=\"true\"",
      "created": 1335106800,
      "updated": 1335106800,
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e"
    },
    {
      "id": "6090ec2daff09e00003db964",
      "text": " ||<",
      "created": 1335106800,
      "updated": 1335106800,
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e"
    },
    {
      "id": "6090ec2daff09e00003db965",
      "text": " ",
      "created": 1335106800,
      "updated": 1335106800,
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e"
    },
    {
      "id": "6090ec2daff09e00003db966",
      "text": " ** 明示的にタイトルを変える方法を用意する",
      "created": 1335106800,
      "updated": 1335106800,
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e"
    },
    {
      "id": "6090ec2daff09e00003db967",
      "text": " lib/termsupport.zshを読む。",
      "created": 1335106800,
      "updated": 1335106800,
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e"
    },
    {
      "id": "6090ec2daff09e00003db968",
      "text": " >||",
      "created": 1335106800,
      "updated": 1335106800,
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e"
    },
    {
      "id": "6090ec2daff09e00003db969",
      "text": " function title {",
      "created": 1335106800,
      "updated": 1335106800,
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e"
    },
    {
      "id": "6090ec2daff09e00003db96a",
      "text": "   [ \"$DISABLE_AUTO_TITLE\" != \"true\" ] || return",
      "created": 1335106800,
      "updated": 1335106800,
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e"
    },
    {
      "id": "6090ec2daff09e00003db96b",
      "text": "   if [[ \"$TERM\" == screen* ]]; then",
      "created": 1335106800,
      "updated": 1335106800,
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e"
    },
    {
      "id": "6090ec2daff09e00003db96c",
      "text": "     print -Pn \"\\ek$1:q\\e\\\\\" #set screen hardstatus, usually truncated at 20 chars",
      "created": 1335106800,
      "updated": 1335106800,
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e"
    },
    {
      "id": "6090ec2daff09e00003db96d",
      "text": "   elif [[ \"$TERM\" == xterm* ]] || [[ $TERM == rxvt* ]] || [[ \"$TERM_PROGRAM\" == \"iTerm.app\" ]]; then",
      "created": 1335106800,
      "updated": 1335106800,
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e"
    },
    {
      "id": "6090ec2daff09e00003db96e",
      "text": "     print -Pn \"\\e]2;$2:q\\a\" #set window name",
      "created": 1335106800,
      "updated": 1335106800,
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e"
    },
    {
      "id": "6090ec2daff09e00003db96f",
      "text": "     print -Pn \"\\e]1;$1:q\\a\" #set icon (=tab) name (will override window name on broken terminal)",
      "created": 1335106800,
      "updated": 1335106800,
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e"
    },
    {
      "id": "6090ec2daff09e00003db970",
      "text": "   fi",
      "created": 1335106800,
      "updated": 1335106800,
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e"
    },
    {
      "id": "6090ec2daff09e00003db971",
      "text": " }",
      "created": 1335106800,
      "updated": 1335106800,
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e"
    },
    {
      "id": "6090ec2daff09e00003db972",
      "text": " ||<",
      "created": 1335106800,
      "updated": 1335106800,
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e"
    },
    {
      "id": "6090ec2daff09e00003db973",
      "text": " そういうDISABLEの仕方をするのはどうか…。呼び出し側でDISABLEするべきだろ…。",
      "created": 1335106800,
      "updated": 1335106800,
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e"
    },
    {
      "id": "6090ec2daff09e00003db974",
      "text": " ",
      "created": 1335106800,
      "updated": 1335106800,
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e"
    },
    {
      "id": "6090ec2daff09e00003db975",
      "text": " いいや、自分で定義しとこう。",
      "created": 1335106800,
      "updated": 1335106800,
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e"
    },
    {
      "id": "6090ec2daff09e00003db976",
      "text": " https://github.com/nishio/dotfiles/commit/cdc7fbc3efd14a3058465cbd102be6d6af7d942a",
      "created": 1335106800,
      "updated": 1335106800,
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e"
    },
    {
      "id": "6090ec2daff09e00003db977",
      "text": " ",
      "created": 1335106800,
      "updated": 1335106800,
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e"
    },
    {
      "id": "6090ec2daff09e00003db978",
      "text": " ** 2012-04-24",
      "created": 1335106800,
      "updated": 1335106800,
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e"
    },
    {
      "id": "6090ec2daff09e00003db979",
      "text": " >||",
      "created": 1335106800,
      "updated": 1335106800,
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e"
    },
    {
      "id": "6090ec2daff09e00003db97a",
      "text": " setopt auto_cd",
      "created": 1335106800,
      "updated": 1335106800,
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e"
    },
    {
      "id": "6090ec2daff09e00003db97b",
      "text": " setopt auto_pushd",
      "created": 1335106800,
      "updated": 1335106800,
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e"
    },
    {
      "id": "6090ec2daff09e00003db97c",
      "text": " ",
      "created": 1335106800,
      "updated": 1335106800,
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e"
    },
    {
      "id": "6090ec2daff09e00003db97d",
      "text": " autoload predict-on",
      "created": 1335106800,
      "updated": 1335106800,
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e"
    },
    {
      "id": "6090ec2daff09e00003db97e",
      "text": " predict-on",
      "created": 1335106800,
      "updated": 1335106800,
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e"
    },
    {
      "id": "6090ec2daff09e00003db97f",
      "text": " ||<",
      "created": 1335106800,
      "updated": 1335106800,
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e"
    },
    {
      "id": "6090ec2daff09e00003db980",
      "text": " predict-onしたらいままで「CUIとはこういうものだ」と思い込んでいた既成概念がガラガラと崩れ落ちた。",
      "created": 1335106800,
      "updated": 1335106800,
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e"
    },
    {
      "id": "6090ec2daff09e00003db981",
      "text": " ",
      "created": 1335106800,
      "updated": 1335106800,
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e"
    },
    {
      "id": "6090ec2daff09e00003db982",
      "text": " ** 2012-04-26",
      "created": 1335106800,
      "updated": 1335106800,
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e"
    },
    {
      "id": "6090ec2daff09e00003db983",
      "text": " ",
      "created": 1335106800,
      "updated": 1335106800,
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e"
    },
    {
      "id": "6090ec2daff09e00003db984",
      "text": " predict-onは成功している時はとても快適だが",
      "created": 1335106800,
      "updated": 1335106800,
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e"
    },
    {
      "id": "6090ec2daff09e00003db985",
      "text": " ",
      "created": 1335106800,
      "updated": 1335106800,
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e"
    },
    {
      "id": "6090ec2daff09e00003db986",
      "text": " - lsって打ってEnter押した時にls foobarがpredictされててlsに失敗する ",
      "created": 1335106800,
      "updated": 1335106800,
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e"
    },
    {
      "id": "6090ec2daff09e00003db987",
      "text": " - less ../fooをしたかったのにless ..まで打った時点でピリオドを含むカレントディレクトリのファイルbar.bazがpredictされて、その後/を入力した時点で../に戻ればいいのにba/になりやがる ",
      "created": 1335106800,
      "updated": 1335106800,
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e"
    },
    {
      "id": "6090ec2daff09e00003db988",
      "text": " - そしてbaだけ消して..に変えようかと思ったら全部消える ",
      "created": 1335106800,
      "updated": 1335106800,
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e"
    },
    {
      "id": "6090ec2daff09e00003db989",
      "text": " - echo \"joo\"としたくてecho \"jまで入力した時点でecho \"deps.js\"をpredictして、そのままooを入力したらjoに戻ればいいのにdooになる。 ",
      "created": 1335106800,
      "updated": 1335106800,
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e"
    },
    {
      "id": "6090ec2daff09e00003db98a",
      "text": " ",
      "created": 1335106800,
      "updated": 1335106800,
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e"
    },
    {
      "id": "6090ec2daff09e00003db98b",
